cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper deals with predicting human interaction from partially observed videos, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model uses deep recurrent neural networks, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of attention mechanisms, which is a popular research topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
